    "description": "Is there any vegetable more versatile than the beets native to the northern regions? Packed with nutrients and bursting with flavor, they enhance most every meal. One little known usage of the vegetable, however, is as a dye for other foods. Why settle for tepid browns and unappetizing greys when you can bask in vibrant reds and deep purples? I plan to create a series of dishes around these colors and need many barrels of beets to bring my vision to life.",
